Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:10.99,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:39.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As a plan to get a strategic upper \Nhand against the Clover Kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:42.02,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Diamond Kingdom attacked \Nthe border town of Kiten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:46.10,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But the Golden Dawn arrived \Nthere before anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.40,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and faced off with the Diamond army,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.28,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,quelling the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.99,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Magic: Swift White Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:03.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I saw a familiar little speck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.87,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:11.17,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you're so beat up means...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.83,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You got stronger again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.83,0:01:14.78,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:16.68,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not losing to you, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:20.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking! You got \Ncrazy strong, too, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:23.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose either, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:36.70,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}Behind the Mask
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:02.84,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm... Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See? No problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.42,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It looks like you're \Nas reckless as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.34,italics,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yuno's actually smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:21.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I think you got a little taller \Nsince I last saw you, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:27.56,italics,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? He always acts \Napathetic when he's with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:30.31,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I might've grown \Nfour or five centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:33.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How do you keep getting taller so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I'm not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:39.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get 20 centimeters taller \Nby tomorrow and look down on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:40.85,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:46.49,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Yuno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:50.42,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, who the heck is this twerp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:59.63,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting all apathetic again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that fussy, \Nmysterious little critter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Sylph I've heard so much about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:10.72,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Yuno make that face! \NIs this the power of the Sylph?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:14.47,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! Who is this mummified shrimp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:15.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're small, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:18.61,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's a guy I used to live with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.07,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.28,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You lived with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:29.56,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We would eat together, study together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:32.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...sleep in the same bed together, \Nand even bathe together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:41.76,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Slept in the same bed... and even bathed...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.59,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Sneaky, sneaky, sneaky, sneaky...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.26,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.08,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:52.44,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thank you so much for \Nsaving my meal last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:54.77,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:04.61,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the girl from back then...\NFrom the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.54,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy this after-battle snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:12.45,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even thrown in some extra dragees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.05,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:20.10,italics,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Now who's this insolent child?\NShe's clearly head over heels for Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:23.59,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Charmy. May I call you "Yuno"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.13,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.16,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.29,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:28.59,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:32.60,italics,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,But my Sylph senses are telling me that \Nshe doesn't actually pose a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.56,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for pushing you \Ndown so suddenly back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.55,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:44.28,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about that! It's just \Nsomething that did indeed happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:48.45,italics,bell,0000,0000,0000,,P-Push... P-Pushed down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.51,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:54.58,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... You must've used some \Nsneaky spell to seduce Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.16,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,You snot-nosed little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.83,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La? What's this creature?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.17,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Charmy! She's a spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.76,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.93,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno belongs to me, dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:12.24,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,"Snot-nosed little brat"? \NI can't let that slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.91,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nineteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.94,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm older than Yuno and \Nrather sophisticated, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.44,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My sexiness doesn't need \Nany magical enhancement!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:24.44,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Sexy?! You're built like a grade-schooler, \Nbesides your giant forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.94,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?! Oh, you did {\i1}not{\i0} just go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:30.24,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,You're also built like a grade-schooler \Nand have a giant forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:35.30,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?! I'll show you \Nwhat happens when you cross a Sylph!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:39.21,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:49.26,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fry you up and eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.68,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.82,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here, you little insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Miz Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:58.66,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Bell, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.23,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.12,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, looks like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.38,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Let me join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:08.88,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:11.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is my senior from \Nthe Black Bulls, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You guys haven't met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.47,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:18.12,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Not like I'd catch the \Neye of an elite from the Golden—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.12,top,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:21.79,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... If it isn't my big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:26.42,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long! I never \Ndreamed I'd run into you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.26,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:33.40,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,What's the black sheep of our family,\N who can barely even fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:35.10,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,even doing on the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:39.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral, who's that rude little twerp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:40.52,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He's my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:45.69,top,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Vice Captain of the \NGolden Dawn, Langris Vaude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:47.32,sign_11079_109_Golden_Dawn_Vice,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(777,1)}Golden Dawn Vice Captain\N{\fs30}Langris Vaude
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:50.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What? Vice captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:54.84,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still acting as the  \NBlack Bulls' pack mule, Finral?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.69,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I'll have to be the next head
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:01.54,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,of the Vaude family, \Nsince you're such a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Get over yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,At the Underwater Temple,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:10.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,it was only because I had Finral's help \Nthat we were able to defeat the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:15.48,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You mean you were actually \Nuseful for once in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:19.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, how can you talk to \Nyour big brother like that, you punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.52,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you address the Vice Captain \Nof the Golden Dawn like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:31.67,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Asta. He's only telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:34.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.29,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,We've already cleaned up\N most of the enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:42.79,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, our captain dealt \Nwith most of them himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:46.28,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,The Bulls aren't needed here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.67,main,Lanbris,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.46,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,When did the Black Bulls \Nbecome a daycare center?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:56.01,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Looking after two children must be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:59.85,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you embarrassed at having \Nto babysit those two rugrats?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling a rugrat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:05.81,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the charms of a mature woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:05.81,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a little kid, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:10.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris, you can insult me \Nto your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:12.36,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:16.61,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But... don't you dare insult the \Nmembers of my Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:20.91,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Who knew you could look so scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.89,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:40.51,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,On the honor of the Eight Shining Generals, \NI'm taking your head back home with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:43.64,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear... You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.31,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:49.02,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,my spatial magic is going\N to hit those civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.04,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,You can't lay a finger on me, Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:57.20,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.08,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:08.53,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. They'll just have to be noble \Nsacrifices for the sake of our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How can you even think about \Nabandoning our citizens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.80,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,And if this goes on, we'll just \Nend up with even more victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:24.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm not gonna abandon anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Finral! Miz Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.36,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:28.20,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.72,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:39.02,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,What can you possibly do \Nin the condition you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:43.33,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a lively retreat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:47.40,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton Creation Magic: Fluffy Sheep Cushion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:59.34,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?! \NStay out of this, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.67,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,Spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:28.29,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! My magic disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.41,main,Yagos,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do, you brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I owe you one, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:05.87,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Your fighting style's \Nas insane as ever, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:09.37,italics,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's smiling again! Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.91,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Langris...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:16.48,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I can't beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:21.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls will beat the Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:22.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:31.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Man, your world tree magic \Nis as impressive as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:33.75,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:38.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm someone who believes his gut instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Vangeance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:44.70,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take off that mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Vangeance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:59.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take off that mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:04.11,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a face that most \Npeople would want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:07.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you, like, super ugly \Nunder there or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I promise I won't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.62,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I know what this is, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:19.15,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,You suspect that I may be the leader of \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:28.26,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,His light magic and your world \Ntree magic are obviously different,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:30.45,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but something's really bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:35.54,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Their builds, their voices, and more \Nthan anything, their ki feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.84,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:39.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's been about ten \Nyears since I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:40.67,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:45.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We met on the battlefield, and after that, \Nwe fought together from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:48.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Then we became captains at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:51.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel's braid shook like \Ncrazy when that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we're best buds or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.69,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but we go back pretty far, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:00.55,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I feel something similar in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:03.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So just let me see your face, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:06.95,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:28.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's one hell of a scar. \NDid you get it on the battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:30.80,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was born with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.60,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,They called me a cursed child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,A cursed child?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:36.76,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Even magic couldn't fix this scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:40.53,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,It creeped out the people around me,\N and they came to fear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.36,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I was the illegitimate \Nchild of a certain noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:47.27,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I lived in the Forsaken Realm\N until I was eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:54.41,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,But following the loss of that noble's heir,\NI was taken in as an aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:59.87,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, I had great magical power,\Nand my world tree magic was viewed with awe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:04.28,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,But even there, they loathed my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:07.38,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, my foster mother \Nbrutally abused me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:11.40,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,It was a hellish childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You sure had it rough, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:19.54,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,But in the midst of all that,\NI met Master Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:24.40,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't care about my appearance.\NAll he saw was my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:35.96,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy, what kind of magic is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.91,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's world tree magic, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:42.87,flashback,julius,0000,0000,0000,,World tree magic?! How sublime and majestic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:43.71,flashback,julius,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:52.42,flashback,julius,0000,0000,0000,,Most of all... It's as though your \Nkindness is trying to protect everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:53.97,flashback,julius,0000,0000,0000,,What wonderful magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:59.22,flashback,julius,0000,0000,0000,,You should definitely join the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.01,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:05.25,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I would love to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:08.48,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,I never even thought about \Njoining the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:11.82,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,But my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.21,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.70,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:22.71,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It really is nothing to worry about, \Nbut if you {\i1}are{\i0} so worried about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.54,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.05,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you this mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:36.57,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,Master Julius, this is so... tacky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:39.59,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But it's my best work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.87,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:45.40,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to pledge my \Ngrimoire to his service.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.90,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This story sounds pretty familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.69,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The lines of his face also look like Licht's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:56.41,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't sense the slightest \Ntrace of magic from his scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:17:00.69,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem to be doing anything tricky \Nwith magic or showing me an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.29,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And more than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:05.67,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,His ki tells me he's not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.58,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this was just some odd coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:14.25,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm glad I was able to tell you \Nand show you things as they really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.88,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:20.21,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Vangeance! Captain Vangeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:22.02,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,The Diamonds have begun to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:25.30,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. There's no need to \Npursue those who are fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.82,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Could you concentrate on helping the injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.23,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:33.05,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go, too? There are \Nplenty of captives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:35.13,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be a pain \Ntransporting them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:36.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:39.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if we're transporting captives,\NI brought some useful guys along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work 'em to the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.62,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Within reason, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:47.09,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if a cute girl is talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:50.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the fighting has calmed down, \Nso why don't we meet up with Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:51.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.89,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?! Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see ya, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:58.21,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you, Asta. Don't eat\Nstuff you find lying on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:02.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd do that! I mean, I used to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:05.48,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Um, c-could I maybe ask for your address?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.60,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from Yuno, you thieving raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.90,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La! Scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.16,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Your scales are getting in my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.78,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.77,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fry you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.20,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.20,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.41,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,You little insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.70,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:25.20,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La! I'm definitely going \Nto fry you up next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.33,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's too late to take it back now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:33.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,but the worst squad just picked \Na fight with the best squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Does your stomach hurt, Finral?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna hurry up and practice with my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:44.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk with Yuno more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.19,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to eat my sorrows away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:49.52,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are way too laid-back! I mean,\NI'm the one who picked the fight, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:53.72,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Here, eat this. Nomity noms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:57.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.92,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what a vulgar bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:10.05,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more careful about \Nwho you associate with, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.17,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you embarrassed to be seen with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.48,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.79,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought that, not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:23.68,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of Asta, and he's my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.77,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Rival? That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:31.52,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Rival in what? Are you guys \Ncompeting for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:33.44,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:38.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Asta, was it okay to \Njust leave so abruptly like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.29,0:19:40.92,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That handsome guy is your \Nold friend, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:41.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet on some other battlefield, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:46.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.25,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...we're both working to \Nbecome the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.60,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:56.81,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,You really aren't embarrassed \Nto say that at all, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:20:01.02,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you peasants don't\N even feel embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:05.22,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect no less from the great peasant \Nwho was chosen by the four-leaf grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:10.14,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?! I won't \Nallow you to make fun of Yuno—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:14.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,There's no rule that says commoners \Ncan't become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:15.55,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:19.16,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,So first, I'll become the \NCaptain of the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:25.11,main,Langris,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Meaning you're completely \Nignoring my existence as vice captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.63,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, things are taken care of over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.52,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,All the wounded are taken care of, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.12,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:38.63,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,The Diamond forces have retreated,\Nand we've taken a number of captives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.13,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Kiten was successfully defended.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.91,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.01,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Please see to the repair \Nof the damaged buildings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.86,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,and set up shelters immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.18,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:50.17,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... I don't think that was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.67,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,a serious attempt by the Diamonds \Nto invade our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.14,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,So what were they after?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:07.03,main,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,I see... The Sylph, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.16,main,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,Offensive spatial magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:13.66,main,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and world tree magic \Nthat uses others' magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:19.24,main,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the rusty old generals of the \Nprevious era had their useful moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.83,main,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,but from here on out, this era belongs
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.55,main,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,to us Mage Warriors, the new generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:04.17,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:03.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.86,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:07.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:09.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Sylph I've heard so much about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:12.17,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Yuno make that face!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:13.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the power of the Sylph?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:16.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a guy I used to live with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:18.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:20.12,flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
